                    <span>This book was actually pretty interesting to read. If you've ever been curious about what the history is behind all those popular candy bars you eat, how they're made and who owns the companies, I defenetly recomend this book. The greatest thing about this book is that its not just some documentary rattling off facts about the topic, it tells a story, it'll keep you reading on, and it's all about chocolate. </span>
                  
